Poker, (Srednio) Zaawansowane Programownie w C++

To compile you need SCons, Python3.4 and boost installed.
You can specify path in src/SConstruct file.
When ready run (inside src folder):

to build everything
$ scons

to build only server:
$ scons pokerd
or (on Windows):
$ scons pokerd.exe

to build only client:
$ scons pokerc
or (on Windows):
$ scons pokerc.exe

to generate code documentation (need doxygen installed)
$ scons doc
